==English==
===Etymology===
From Latin ''[[#Latin|ichneumon]]'', from Greek ''[[ἰχνευμων]]'' literally ‘tracker’, from ''[[ἴχνος]]'' ‘track, footprint’.

===Pronunciation===
{{IPA|/ɪkˈnju:mən/}}

